# API Rules

- All requests go through `src/lib/api.ts`
- Use only: `apiGet`, `apiPost`, `apiPut`, `apiDelete`
- No raw `fetch` or `axios.create`

- No API calls in components or MyComponents
- Use `src/services/*` for domain logic

- No duplicate API wrappers
- No `any` in service contracts
- Map DTO → UI model in service layer

- Screens must not contain large API orchestration